{% doc %}
  @prompt
    make a best seller module  adding products from the catalog 
    
    product photo
    Title
    Description 
    Price
    Available colors
    
    Everything has to be easy to adjustable., it has an slider function and move automatic every 10 seconds, it can be turned off., do not show navigation in mobile version. 
    
    add adjustments for the  navigation buttons 
    
    the image and the title gonna redirect to the product page of each product., remove the pagination control, do not show arrows in the slider, the photo and the product title should be linked to the product page, add weight for Typography options 
    Card padding can be 0, The maximum area for the content is 1500px

{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
